Hentai inspector here. I have been requested to review this doujin, and after reading everything from start to finish, while deciding the quality, here is my evaluations. Most noticable is the artworks, it is very good and detailed, more than so, close to looking like a casual manga artworks, which is pleasing to say the least. There's not that many scenes of different actions, but there's various positions, which is totally fine based on my evaluation. Also, there's a lot of panels that greatly focuses on specific sections, which is a bonus in term of space management, while still engaging with the story. The story is pretty simple, yet the author still managed to pull a good amount of pages into it, without having to repeat nor insert unnecessary stuff. But it is very clear that this is not for the weak minded that are not prepared to learn how fiction works, which makes this less appealing to some. But disregarding the genre, I will give this a 8/10.
